The paper deals with time series data mining and clustering, which are common topics in machine learning and data mining. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses measures of similarity and association, which are relevant to cs.DM (Data Mining) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The proposed methods for constructing association measures involve mathematical techniques, which are related to cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
